OL,3,CGuernsey Chief Minister calls for
OL,4,Cresignation of disgraced politician
OL,6,FOne of the main issues is that the law
OL,7,Fdoes not provide an adequate way to
OL,8,Fremove Le Tocq as a States Member, or
OL,9,Fremove him without pay.
OL,11,F"The Reform Law is not an easy law to
OL,12,Fchange," Deputy de Sausmarez
OL,13,Fexplained. "I'd reiterate that I'm
OL,14,Fstill hoping that Le Tocq will choose
OL,15,Fto do the right thing, but it is right
OL,16,Fthat we also consider whether our laws
OL,17,Fand our other rules around this need
OL,18,Fto change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
