OL,3,CGuernsey Chief Minister calls for
OL,4,Cresignation of disgraced politician
OL,6,F"I don't think we should be making
OL,7,Fknee-jerk reactions on what is a very
OL,8,Femotional and difficult period. It
OL,9,Fneeds a serious and careful
OL,10,Fconsideration."
OL,12,FRichard Graham, a political
OL,13,Fcommentator who served with Le Tocq in
OL,14,Fthe States, also believes that he
OL,15,Fshould do the "honourable thing" and
OL,16,Fresign.
OL,18,F"I would be immensely surprised if his
OL,19,Ffirst reaction isn't to resign as a
OL,20,FDeputy," he explained.
