OL,6,F"I can't imagine that he would come to
OL,7,Fthe conclusion that he could possibly
OL,8,Fcarry on serving.
OL,10,F"I think that it would be extremely
OL,11,Funfortunate for politics in Guernsey
OL,12,F(if he did), and I think enormous
OL,13,Fpressure would be brought on him to
OL,14,Fthink again."
OL,16,FLe Tocq's resignation or removal as a
OL,17,FStates Member once sentenced will
OL,18,Ftrigger the island's first-ever by-
OL,19,Felection under the island-wide voting
OL,20,Fsystem.
