OL,4,Cresignation of disgraced politician
OL,6,FDeputy de Sausmarez told ITV News that
OL,7,Fone of the first States Assembly
OL,8,Fdebates this political term determined
OL,9,Fa by-election would be "significantly
OL,10,Fless costly than the original
OL,11,Festimates suggested".
OL,13,FThe Chief Minister also explained that
OL,14,Fvetting procedures would go some way
OL,15,Fto rebuilding trust in the States
OL,16,Ffollowing Le Tocq's guilty pleas.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
