OL,3,CGuernsey Chief Minister calls for
OL,4,Cresignation of disgraced politician
OL,6,F"The actions of one individual are not
OL,7,Freflective of the government of the
OL,8,FStates as a whole. What really matters
OL,9,Fis how we respond to those actions.
OL,11,F"I think we can take a silver lining
OL,12,Ffrom this awful situation, it is that
OL,13,Fwe have seen that nobody is above the
OL,14,Flaw, no matter how senior. No matter
OL,15,Ftheir status, they can be held to
OL,16,Fproper and just account."
